// Bike Medic — bmd_* keys. Phase 1: English-only canonical key set.
// {{interpolation}} (e.g. {{n}}, {{sym}}, {{val}}) is substituted at render time.
// Brand / tool names (DeftBrain, deftbrain.com, BuyWise, Decision Coach) stay
// verbatim in every language. The "— Generated by DeftBrain · deftbrain.com"
// suffix is added in code via BRAND — not in keys. Emoji rendered in JSX next
// to a label stays OUT of the string; emoji embedded inside a value is kept in.
//
// Domain identifiers (problem ids, fix ids, tree node ids, bike-type values,
// tool inventory canonical names) are sent to the backend / used as comparison
// keys and stay English in the component data — only the DISPLAYED labels are
// keyed here. The canonical tool-inventory names double as backend identifiers,
// so they are matched case-insensitively against owned-tool keys; their display
// labels are keyed under bmd_inv_*.
